# MongoDB Atlas connection string
# How to get it:
#   1. Go to https://cloud.mongodb.com
#   2. Create a free M0 cluster (no credit card needed)
#   3. Database Access → add a user with a password
#   4. Network Access → add 0.0.0.0/0 to allow Vercel's IPs
#   5. Connect → Drivers → copy the connection string
#   6. Replace <password> with your actual database user password
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/feedback-flow
